title: Charlaine Harris-A Fool And His Honey
description: Aurora' s been around long enough to know that when a day starts out with your handyman going crazy in your front yard, it probably won' t get any better. Sure enough, her husband Martin' s niece Regina shows up with a baby whom no one knew she was expecting. Then she disappears, leaving behind the child-- and a murdered husband. To find her, Roe and Martin retrace her steps from sunny Georgia back to snowy Ohio, where they will uncover dark family secrets-- at their own peril
